OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe a mostly fine and dry day, with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and bright
OL,8,For sunny spells. Chance of a few light
OL,9,Fshowers into the afternoon. Breezy
OL,10,Falong the coast and feeling rather
OL,11,Fcool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,14,Flargely dry night, with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud and occasional clear
OL,16,Fspells. Turning increasingly cloudy
OL,17,Ffrom the south by dawn. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
