OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cloudy start with some light
OL,6,Fshowers. The cloud breaking up to give
OL,7,Fsome bright or sunny spells into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, with further showers,
OL,9,Flocally heavy. Feeling warm in
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,13,Fand dry with warm sunny spells
OL,14,FSaturday. A band of rain clearing
OL,15,Fsouth early on Sunday, with brighter
OL,16,Fskies following. Further showers
OL,17,FMonday. Often breezy and feeling
OL,18,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
